## ğŸ“¦ Installation
**From PyPI**  
```bash
pip install paz-cli
```

**From Source**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/MahdiMirshafiee/password-analyzer-cli
cd password-analyzer-cli
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate       # Linux/macOS
# venv\Scripts\activate        # Windows PowerShell
pip install -e .
```
